Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來一發射線喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這射線真是越來越性感了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}白色月姬  Phantas  Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic  Circuit  Fullcount  大回轉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marble  Phantasm！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紳士怪人  松旺子武君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又遇到了大危機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被嫉妒所附體的妖怪赤髮女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy85\fscx85\pos(416,330)}秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然開始將鍋子當成化妝品來賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再來花言巧語了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此刻出現了意外的救星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  蓮  你要拿那蒟蒻幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  白色月姬  Phantas  Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行政改革
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回也要讓你的心Marble  Phantasm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法少女題材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為人類少女的時光只不過是一瞬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}心跳！Melty  Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴  來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野君  這是速食咖哩  而且裡面還是冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要讓大腦得到休息的話  放鬆是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…和哥哥在海邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴先生  要麥茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴少爺  這樣下去皮膚會「把」太陽曬傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哈哈哈  該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是養眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  雖然是來玩  但你好歹是遠野家長男  像樣點好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.07,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}私人海灘  閒人免進  遠野家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這裡之後你就一直在傻笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有在想奇怪的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我放手你這笨蛋吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的啊  放手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日特別企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野家主辦  心跳沙灘排球大會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那啥啊志貴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天啊  夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女傭也不再是女傭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了我也「被」女僕裝脫掉  變回女人的季節了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為各位的心都生銹了  所以才要用運動來加深感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  把球砸進對方的領地裡就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道沙灘排球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發球的台詞是Potemkin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得分之後是Gal  Undo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是常識
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以教壞別人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是玩  小規則就不用在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就來抽籤分成兩組吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝的一隊有優勝團體獎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有個人獎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\1c&000000&\shad0\fs17\fscx80\pos(480,250)}優勝隊伍  秋田小町米一年份\N最佳射手獎  鬼戰車  T-34\N沙灘女王獎  碗刷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這次的MVP可以得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供和志貴先生在單間一起過夜的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  琥珀  這種沒羞恥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為各種失誤  食物和房間都只預定了一份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在趕快去重新準備  如果出什麼事就太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動萬能的秋葉小姐只要拿到MVP就能保住志貴先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你成為MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有兩人還是有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這種事  我很開心喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我必須得做點什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒沒沒沒什麼啊  哦呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就開始抽籤分隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}白隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  居然和雪兒一起  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要敬謝不敏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外…外國人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照了  都古小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩味好重  這個是印度人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}紅隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心  我會「被」加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最佳陣容  根據我的計算  敗率是0
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為能接下我的發球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Potemkin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gal  Undo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹扣殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  球還沒出界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我笑納了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都古小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都古
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能在拳上看到怎樣的將來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父！

Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣真背
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪兒快看  球還沒出界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  接給你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MVP  MVP  MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘了  反射性地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gal  Undo！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止都還在計算之內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼計算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一口氣決定勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡門頂肘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:08:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才修好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止都還在計算之內
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪兒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該來個大招了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這根本就是犯規啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gal  Undo！
